{"tid":2062754,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公民黨向歐盟提出延長【特區護照持有人】免簽逗留期及申請工作簽證等待遇","createTime":"2020-06-13T10:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T15:25:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"665cb8eea0ae9af134acd143b077c45452dcb919","tid":2062754,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T10:58:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531885-20200613.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531885-20200613.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrlDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=cc41a506\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531885-20200613.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=15194366\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531885-20200613.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n公民黨表示，正就香港市民簽證權益向歐盟提出5項建議，包括延長免簽證逗留期限、保證反修例運動構成的刑事罪行不會影響批發簽證、鼓勵歐盟的學術及職業訓練機構取錄香港學生、降低特區護照持有人在歐盟申請工作簽證的門檻等。<br />\n<br />\n黨魁楊岳橋表示，不少歐洲議員都對建議構思有興趣，會繼續提出具體措施。他又說，爭取簽證權利一直是特區政府的工作，不擔心建議會等同於「勾結外國勢力」。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨東區區議員鄭達鴻說，目的是為了協助1997年後出生，持有特區護照的香港市民，可享多一項保障，有關建議並非鼓勵年輕人離開香港，只是希望提供更多選擇。"},{"pid":"5f7a9085ff8f54fce5fe91df92859bc0aa187ac6","tid":2062754,"uid":55458,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你班連登狗仲話攬炒喎"},{"pid":"28b02f8b7989de130e2d45bb2a713a83e26a89b3","tid":2062754,"uid":266342,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:03:02.000Z","msg":"on9，根本應該取消免簽證"},{"pid":"bab7edf0a3d3f92fd50a1e5344a9d5d08905dd2a","tid":2062754,"uid":79563,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"28b02f8b7989de130e2d45bb2a713a83e26a89b3","tid":2062754,"uid":266342,